config.description: Hybrid-Optimized strategy for E8 prop firm challenge - balanced ROI and safety

MonteCarloAgent.description: Real-time Monte Carlo simulation - runs 1000+ simulations per trade to assess risk before execution

MultiTimeframeAgent.description: Confirms signals across M5/M15/H1/H4/D1 timeframes - prevents trading against higher TF trend

VolumeLiquidityAgent.description: Detects institutional flows and dangerous spread widening - protects from slippage

SupportResistanceAgent.description: Trades bounces at support/resistance and confirmed breakouts - improves entry/exit precision

DivergenceAgent.description: Catches RSI/MACD divergence for early trend reversal signals
